==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ortalidian
<hw>Or`ta*lid"i*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of numerous small two-winged flies of the family
<fam>Ortalidae</fam>. The larvae of many of these flies live in fruit;
those of others produce galls on various plants.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Orthid</ent>⟦br⟧
